        <entry>
            <title>Migration from oracle to postgres</title>
            <link href="https://blog.rockdata.net/posts/practice/oracle-to-postgres/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"  hreflang="en" />
            <id>https://blog.rockdata.net/posts/practice/oracle-to-postgres/</id>
                    <author>
                        <name>Linn Shawn</name>
                    </author>
            <published>2022-05-20T09:00:00+02:00</published>
            <updated>2022-05-29T10:25:15+08:00</updated>
            <content type="html">
                &lt;p&gt;The toughest things happened in migration from oracle to postgres:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The famous &lt;a
  class=&#34;gblog-markdown__link&#34;
  href=&#34;https://www.modb.pro/db/82136&#34;
  
&gt;ERROR: current transaction is aborted, commands ignored until end of transaction block&lt;/a&gt;, and some discussion in community&amp;rsquo;s pgsql-hackers group: &lt;a
  class=&#34;gblog-markdown__link&#34;
  href=&#34;https://www.postgresql.org/message-id/flat/0A3221C70F24FB45833433255569204D1F6A9286%40G01JPEXMBYT05&#34;
  
&gt;Statement-level rollback&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CNBC&amp;rsquo;s Eugene Kim posted &lt;a
  class=&#34;gblog-markdown__link&#34;
  href=&#34;https://www.cnbc.com/2018/10/23/amazon-move-off-oracle-caused-prime-day-outage-in-warehouse.html&#34;
  
&gt;Amazon’s move off Oracle caused Prime Day outage in one of its biggest warehouses, internal report says&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amazon&amp;rsquo;s Baji Shaik, Deepak Mahto, and Sudip Acharya posted &lt;a
  class=&#34;gblog-markdown__link&#34;
  href=&#34;https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/database/convert-the-number-data-type-from-oracle-to-postgresql-part-1/&#34;
  
&gt;Convert the NUMBER data type from Oracle to PostgreSQL – Part 1&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amazon&amp;rsquo;s Baji Shaik, Deepak Mahto, and Sudip Acharya posted &lt;a
  class=&#34;gblog-markdown__link&#34;
  href=&#34;https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/database/convert-the-number-data-type-from-oracle-to-postgresql-part-2/&#34;
  
&gt;Convert the NUMBER data type from Oracle to PostgreSQL – Part 2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some migration experience:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Venkata B Nagothi&amp;rsquo;s experience on migration: &lt;a
  class=&#34;gblog-markdown__link&#34;
  href=&#34;https://www.pgconf.asia/JA/2016/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/pgConf-Asia-Japan.pdf&#34;
  
&gt;Migrations to PostgreSQL from Oracle&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

            </content>  
